'''Reginald Lannister''' is a minor character in the [[Season 2|second season]]. He is played by [[Patrick Fitzsymons]] and only appears in &quot;[[The Ghost of Harrenhal]].&quot; Reginald Lannister is an officer in the army of House Lannister. He is a distant relative of Lord [[Tywin Lannister]] and is sent home to the [[Westerlands]] for insubordination.
